FT  07 DEC 94 / Observer: Acidic
Uncharitable suggestion from derivatives buffs yesterday. Californian
taxpayers living in the area south of Los Angeles and who are staring at
Dollars 1.5bn plus of losses on the region's investment portfolio as a
result of dealings by one Robert Citron - the treasurer who quit at the
beginning of the week - might care to rename their domicile Lemon County.
